---

<BaseLayout
  title="ひろとのおすすめ本【副業×FIRE×投資】"
  description="シングル父ひろとが実際に読んでよかった本をまとめています。楽天・Amazonリンクあり。"
>
  <div class="books-page">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">トップ</a>
      <span>›</span>
      <span>おすすめ本</span>
    </nav>

    <header class="books-hero">
      <p class="books-eyebrow">Recommended Books</p>
      <h1>ひろとのおすすめ本【副業×FIRE×投資】</h1>
      <p>
        シングル父として、お金・副業・FIREを考える中で実際に読んでよかった本をまとめました。
        まずは考え方の土台を作ってくれた本から、順番に置いています。
      </p>
    </header>
    <div class="book-sections">
      {sections.map((section, index) => (
        <section class="book-section">
          <div class="book-section-head">
            <span class="book-index">{String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            <div>
              <h2>{section.title}</h2>
              <p>{section.note}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="book-list">
            {section.books.map((book) => (
              <article class="book-card">
                <img src={book.cover} alt={book.title} class="book-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="book-body">
                  <div class="book-headline">
                    <h3>{book.title}</h3>
                    <span class="pr-badge">PR</span>
                  </div>
                  {book.author && <p class="book-author">{book.author}</p>}
                  <p>{book.body}</p>
                  <a
                    href={book.rakuten}
                    class="book-link"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer"
                  >
                    楽天で見る（PR）
                  </a>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.books-page {
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.books-hero {
  padding: 34px 0 28px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.books-eyebrow {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  color: var(--color-accent);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.books-hero h1 {
  margin: 0 0 16px;
  font-size: 2rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
  letter-spacing: 0;
}

.books-hero p {
  max-width: 760px;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.9;
}

.book-sections {
  display: grid;
  gap: 34px;
}

.book-section {
  padding: 26px 0 30px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.book-section-head {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 54px 1fr;
  gap: 18px;
  align-items: start;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.book-index {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
  color: var(--color-accent);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.book-section h2 {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  letter-spacing: 0;
}

.book-section-head p {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.book-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
}

.book-card {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 128px 1fr;
  gap: 18px;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 18px;
  background: #fff;
}

.book-cover {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}

.book-headline {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.book-body h3 {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--color-text);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

.book-author {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.book-body p {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.pr-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 42px;
  height: 24px;
  padding: 0 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  color: var(--color-accent);
}

.book-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 12px;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  font-weight: 700;
}

@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .books-hero h1 {
    font-size: 1.55rem;
  }

  .book-section-head {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .book-card {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .book-cover {
    max-width: 160px;
  }
}
</style>
